  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Designing the Foundation**\n\nI\'m currently focused on the foundational elements for this web app, particularly its visual identity. I\'m prioritizing the design system implementation, specifically fonts. I\'ve decided on `EB Garamond` for displays and headlines, and `Hanken Grotesk` (or potentially `Inter`, or another classy sans-serif) for the UI. Importing these is next on the agenda.\n\n\n**Defining the Aesthetic**\n\nI\'ve been working on the visual style, adding `EB Garamond` and `Hanken Grotesk` to the `index.css`. The color palette is shaping up to be off-white backgrounds, wooden accent lines, charcoal colors, and a structured, matte grid design. The IndexedDB database structure is now defined with fields for artwork details, including status, notes, and image data (blobs or base64). I\'m planning a gallery interface with grid layouts, filters, a matting effect for previews, and an inviting empty state.\n\n\n**Developing the Interface**\n\nI\'m now deep in the design of the creative workspace, the core of the app. An interactive visualizer frame is key, allowing instant previewing of matte and frame choices. Form fields will allow for changes to the art piece\'s information. I\'m planning to include muted style chips, along with options for frame type, mat size, and artwork dimensions. I\'ll also add state controls, including status buttons and a prominent \"Approve for Production\" button to signify completion.\n\n\n**Implementing Download Options**\n\nI\'m now focusing on export options within the workspace. I envision a \"Download\" button offering multiple choices. First, \"Download High-Res Original\" will download the raw uploaded image. Second, \"Download Framed Mockup\" will create a high-quality preview using HTML5 canvas, showing the framed piece. Also, I will include a downloadable spec sheet (PDF/text) and a \"Download All-In-One Spec Bundle\" for all related data. I\'m checking into making the code highly modular as well.\n\n\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 6
      nanos: 907839814
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
