    web_documents {
      url: "https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF471o3uY-haH8y9XeVJirlCJ3Rp02jXinoX6i6pMoXxrkl4bB3ij77ah6T0y_EMGSGew9GxFpMjnxwd_VlfYUbjKesZDCGeS6lHJnHJoBEcN4Fng6hTDjOJRyaBpTrnqXX7VBvZSOBJ7A0vLpoJnV6XXvoQ9TlB4WB3zioY9rjFZp5f63oEtm_60B0BrrYk5PH"
      title: "endgrate.com"
    }
    summary: "To retrieve a list of all responses for a Google Form using the Google Forms API, you will use the `forms.responses.list()` method. This is a RESTful API endpoint that allows programmatic access to form submission data.[1][2][3]\n\nThe core details for this endpoint are:\n*   **Method**: `GET`[4]\n*   **URL**: `https://forms.googleapis.com/v1/forms/{formId}/responses`[4]\n\n**Path Parameters**:\n*   `formId`: This is a required string that identifies the specific Google Form whose responses you want to list.[4][5]\n\n**Query Parameters (Optional)**:\n*   `filter`: Allows you to specify which form responses to return. Currently, supported filters are `timestamp > N` or `timestamp >= N` to get responses submitted after or at a specific timestamp. The timestamp must be in RFC3339 UTC \"Zulu\" format (e.g., \"2014-10-02T15:01:23Z\").[4]\n*   `pageSize`: Defines the maximum number of responses to return. If unspecified or zero, the service returns a maximum of 5000 responses.[4]\n*   `pageToken`: Used for pagination. If a previous request returned a `nextPageToken`, you can provide it here to retrieve the next page of responses.[4]\n\n**Response Body**:\nThe response will contain a JSON object with:\n*   `responses`: An array of `FormResponse` objects, each representing a submitted response to the form.[4]\n*   `nextPageToken`: If more responses are available beyond the current page, this token will be present. You can use it in a subsequent request to fetch the next set of responses.[4]\n\n**Authorization**:\nAccess to this endpoint requires OAuth 2.0. Your request must include a Bearer access token with appropriate Google Forms API scopes, such as `https://www.googleapis.com/auth/forms.responses.readonly` or `https://www.googleapis.com/auth/forms.body`.[2][4] You will need to enable the Google Forms API in your Google Cloud project and create OAuth credentials (client ID and secret) to obtain an access token.[2][6]\n\nSources:\n[1] [google.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH0B3el5sch1pyt_4wg71yT3FjN13aVzSNckOPd_z7ZrnwHwZp7CkV9rG0undNgyEcAdjH1-bzkv5QLeiObY4y-Br9my2DVAxMh8i032n8ypJ34AQRFJAaJ6oPQfSUZGEZrCLePNZKDj7-qzyOd8fE8UIn5GRlgsz2KXXFEvTkK8kcgs5pqYt1C61Jd6w==)\n[2] [dlthub.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHaVTUf3ND2gWKPeAHQbmu7NrKOewFPdk9BveME5K27v4bp5cosoGhMt_0RU5jdyfy5-bhPtItfb9MxYeDa0HjFjVQhXwu2a_HWE6auwLZKWJhgq-aD66_D13uWsKPY6FVDsqDOQiBVSo4=)\n[3] [googleblog.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEmOO265WbTK8HuDhuX7ZYsTfnMXmyI3TiOZqM8NXtzOCVBrjiKpk0XcdvQwZ_6BtuqSKGg1rEnWq4K10q1LblqTSivvEK7F9PZPoXcufNAJHsH37eoj7_XUIOFn-S53e0nM_91LBfk1prwyic_kBKlqFlsUQy1sZmRvC3Hn1M=)\n[4] [google.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFS3p5IGcAlevB_tP_WB6m6rfDzJZItXkzoSpPria2z-3IlDj07YxOBAmXU4UDXV7MEXTLpVq4aC9zh6fPvIOuR0NzyNkA06vKoczbb_dVLW36L6792SGSXFhZMXy5K-OD1WSHRofeHSdTwsfkfhnKXbAP8BMnG76s9ykYvrxoljHIi2B6R5evB-mf0eVLVXcasOVA=)\n[5] [needle.app](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG628wztpljpZAqd7yXL-WV9x-J23r4ULciPx27sIfCIcfjWqKLydNlw2KCdHT5bIhzuviNfXKDCuoDuPFhzTM4gxJgT5Nw6JW7G5LT6rpwCs0mXuz8ZIdjjQrztJdz47LOvC3wCHzEFid8JI9OW-qsHKsB22F0M57m-QeJKaYNyYC6rtRY86C91aZM3MQxlPSHGgh06AQ=)\n[6] [endgrate.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF471o3uY-haH8y9XeVJirlCJ3Rp02jXinoX6i6pMoXxrkl4bB3ij77ah6T0y_EMGSGew9GxFpMjnxwd_VlfYUbjKesZDCGeS6lHJnHJoBEcN4Fng6hTDjOJRyaBpTrnqXX7VBvZSOBJ7A0vLpoJnV6XXvoQ9TlB4WB3zioY9rjFZp5f63oEtm_60B0BrrYk5PH)"
