    summary: "To list responses from a Google Form using the Forms API with `curl`, you\'ll need your `FORM_ID` and an OAuth 2.0 `ACCESS_TOKEN` with the necessary scopes (e.g., `https://www.googleapis.com/auth/forms.responses.readonly`).[1][2]\n\nThe base URL for the Google Forms API is `https://forms.googleapis.com`.[1][3] The endpoint for listing responses is `/v1/forms/{formId}/responses`, and it uses the `GET` method.[1][3]\n\nHere\'s a `curl` example:\n\n\n\nSources:\n[1] [dlthub.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEN3yUKfs6ZW1TsoHrOOVWT_MAADbLTKRhZh7y6CaQmaJAO3UugM33Unz_hDZspGxPmNRdwKn8fi3TjAZkARMYF0wbwAvSdSyIMB3BcPCFIm09x3Z94f2XDXJQ_LEgJdMsihFRDI4ab7Q==)\n[2] [google.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGJH5jPgB2UZ7Ld4uUbNs9DcFUx52yGqbQ7_L9Vnycvqnmerz1o0WHXqW6hYcHrT7olIak0B8DNxmmguXf0d_M1zOq5mz9KQbIkhDosaRBb0LsaGz70YqAfHguKsf2bX8IaHrCOlD6cOOZRsWq-OU5Qq0Ob1OMMkDsppcSmvE15RttT5NsMabWkUYKIUtYGejCOgg==)\n[3] [google.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQExRD5E16UZ4EumUDLB_sF5zf1l884AOOFKyT7w2qktYexxsMKoWAaRWLgaWYdACiqMclLrvIk_5K6Nu5PaLNgYD9_CGf-sdNp7TosB_EKlnZShhyytP6JvCiwdMe-ssCuAcRAp1idqBzuqOdpPTcLo4rCjJlYinlFmxQ==)"
