    web_documents {
      url: "https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGApl75kGf9_gTz2vlSadd4jmnGn6V3ULAHpYhYt3-WH4Qcxm98gXNvH4QbvtVhBARibPf5kENkOrMj3jllE8GhM0BCBz0Gr2PXA6m5qeM045mniMgRA5E7ZIqAHYXsVZ7Cnmi6YhemYCcyxW3EvG78qh8La-qkMwUfZNAV1j7J0PqyKt8EsyrjicAxYTGEDUMSTHQRA0Js"
      title: "stackoverflow.com"
    }
    summary: "To get the editable form ID from a Google Forms \"viewform\" link, you need to extract a specific part of the URL. The `1FAIpQL` string is typically associated with pre-filled links or form submissions, rather than the main editable form ID.\n\nHere\'s how to obtain the editable form ID and construct the edit link:\n\n**From a \"viewform\" link:**\nThe editable form ID is a long string of characters found within the URL of a Google Form. When you have a \"viewform\" link (the public submission link), the structure is generally like this:\n`https://docs.google.com/forms/d/FORM_ID/viewform`\n\nTo get the editable form ID, you would extract the `FORM_ID` part. For example, if your viewform link is `https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1ABC123DEF456GHI789JKL0MNO_PQR_STUV/viewform`, the editable form ID is `1ABC123DEF456GHI789JKL0MNO_PQR_STUV`[1][2][3].\n\nOnce you have the `FORM_ID`, you can construct the editable link by changing `/viewform` to `/edit`:\n`https://docs.google.com/forms/d/FORM_ID/edit`[1]\n\n**Regarding \"1FAIpQL\":**\nThe string `1FAIpQL` typically appears in pre-filled Google Form URLs or when submitting a form. It is part of the query parameters for specific responses or pre-filled data, not the main form ID that allows you to edit the form\'s structure[4].\n\n**If you are the owner of the form:**\nIf you own the Google Form, the easiest way to get the edit URL is to open the form in your browser, and the URL in the address bar will automatically be the edit URL[1]. You can also achieve this programmatically using Google Apps Script with `FormApp.getActiveForm().getId()` or by opening the form by its URL and then getting its ID[1][5].\n\nSources:\n[1] [stackoverflow.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGaj56Wdr-MEFG0okvXKqTcWv_TEaTHnjGWtO227bYovZD284W4WxEtV0sEdYj5WmTVH_uUmp_kcsW45-ZRT_OrnSebQUsX-fSwz3UrWn962e20OMPpHZp8COVIgS-ymQpn1QH2rgBxX8Yy4WcVGeiuUpxGFdUr6OSyxlxc99EiO3I=)\n[2] [medium.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH0D_Z7BOpIQb8eXerVTXyed-3JsHMwU8x-6dyngsAhlYJZ_Gg4nhWS8dD0h9Mjj86sQNrAlREWo1SK02UKTDadq05F_LvCAU3H3Fdn2ainJhCE29JTJ_Tj29Td-LkZHCGqLlDk6DelIz0KEsz4-IJhTfwyZFiP7lmp890pB8uVdI-PI5cmCjixSIICgi8_LJgBhxqTAQPVrB9M0h4=)\n[3] [stackexchange.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEUugmzkPVdJMGoUcK4V1gfbN9ElKPbKTf51yTTX4MN3JJkGz3gPzaYuHqx6GYCylmn7T8au8ng9WRpoOap0FsefEojPUlcjC43LqgLDRLbUewxj-F2srgL42rLzZc1DJnFjrEqxVCBPIXlH2gltTK4KqOtUFqdi668cYyfG_pWJdiLaFs5ySUn7yRFsmBLNd7cmzMxJuluEXvu6B9LimWgFKKo5Q7iWL52GIvgjyx5_u2lZ1jbINOjcyqQEBg=)\n[4] [stackoverflow.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFmG8QJ4Q-Z78UoGn5-V53vapidTq7HqMoIQ6qrCPCqQbUdyxjYLyUWx9iWJyottHEYRLCPvGIHTA0up4S0QwznxX6DEX1KWIusAuz0gX9msXcS0TA4D9IgHbOxoZ79rNh4RGzr1GgQJ2rSBOKG4h13HMbMBMKOn5bZnpnmIm7RwTlJJqP2ujQUp6XhSH73Z7YMRMT0Tbr-xFnKfkigphtE_nc0dha6iXvK8xycEKsxs4lWdQ==)\n[5] [stackoverflow.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGApl75kGf9_gTz2vlSadd4jmnGn6V3ULAHpYhYt3-WH4Qcxm98gXNvH4QbvtVhBARibPf5kENkOrMj3jllE8GhM0BCBz0Gr2PXA6m5qeM045mniMgRA5E7ZIqAHYXsVZ7Cnmi6YhemYCcyxW3EvG78qh8La-qkMwUfZNAV1j7J0PqyKt8EsyrjicAxYTGEDUMSTHQRA0Js)"
